The aim of this study is to compare weekly-XELIRI(wXELIRI) regimen versus FOLFIRI regimen in the treatment of advanced colorectal cancer patients.

 The hypothesis is the efficacy of wXELIRI is not less than FOLFIRI with tolerable toxicity.

